snippet.title: Sunkenland Gameplay Trailer | Upcoming Survival Game 2023 PC
snippet.description:
#indiegame #survivalgame #gamingnews 
Sunkenland is a Waterworld themed upcoming survival game. Explore sunken cities, build your base, craft items, trade and fight pirates as you struggle to survive on an aquatic post-apocalypse world plagued by hunger and violence.

Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2080690/Sunkenland/
Sunkenland | Upcoming Survival Game 2023
